  countUnit          String? // sale/count unit (e.g. each, ml, g) — defaults to unit when null
  conversionFactor   Float                     @default(1) // sale/count units per purchase unit; purchase cost ÷ factor = sale/count unit cost
  countArea          String? // physical walking-order grouping for stocktake (Bar, Kitchen, Cool room…)
  measurePerCountUnit Float?  // net measurable amount in ONE count/cost unit, e.g. a punnet ≈ 250 (g). Bridges weight/volume recipe lines to count-unit items.
